---
// Partnership
---
<section class="py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-24 bg-brand-primary text-brand-text">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 w-full p-24">
    <!-- CTA Content -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16 md:mb-24 lg:mb-32">
      <!-- Label -->
      <p class="font-sans mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-charcoal-500 text-xs sm:text-sm tracking-wider uppercase">
        A Different Kind of AI Partnership
      </p>
      
      <!-- Headline -->
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl tracking-tight mb-4 sm:mb-6 leading-tight">
        We're AI consultants who guide you to success.
      </h2>
      
      <!-- Subheadline -->
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl font-sans leading-relaxed">
        We only earn when you generate measurable value. Your wins are our wins.
      </p>

    </div>

      <!-- Grid columns -->

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12 auto-rows-fr">
  <!-- First row -->
  <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12 bg-[#e7e5e0] flex flex-col justify-between h-full shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
    <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-charcoal leading-tight">AI Assessment</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Get a clear view of where AI can create the most value in your operations with a tailored, data-driven assessment.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12 bg-[#e7e5e0] flex flex-col justify-between h-full shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
    <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-charcoal leading-tight">High-Impact Opportunity</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">We pinpoint the areas where AI delivers the biggest return—so you can invest time and resources where it truly matters.</p>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Merged column - spans 2 rows on large screens, normal on mobile -->
  <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12 bg-[#e7e5e0] h-full shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300 lg:row-span-2 sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
    <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-charcoal leading-tight">Results-based Fees</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">We don’t get paid until our solutions deliver measurable impact—because your success is the only outcome that matters.</p>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Second row -->
  <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12 bg-[#e7e5e0] flex flex-col justify-between h-full shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
    <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-charcoal leading-tight">Implementation</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">From setup to go-live, we handle integration, training, and real-world implementation to ensure your team is ready and confident.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12 bg-[#e7e5e0] flex flex-col justify-between h-full shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
    <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl mb-3 sm:mb-4 text-charcoal leading-tight">Strategic Guidance</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Our experts stay with you post-launch, providing insights, improvements, and dedicated support as your business evolves.</p>
  </div>
</div>
      
      
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
